xxl.core.indexStructures.rtrees

Class RtreeIterativeBulkloader<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • xxl.core.indexStructures.rtrees.AbstractIterativeRtreeBulkloader<T>
      • xxl.core.indexStructures.rtrees.RtreeIterativeBulkloader<T>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IterativeBulkLoaderInterface<T>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    RtreeIterativeBulkloader.MainMemoryCollectionBulkLoader, RtreeIterativeBulkloader.RtreeIterativeBulkloaderAsynch

    public class RtreeIterativeBulkloader<T>
extends AbstractIterativeRtreeBulkloader<T>
    This class implements level by level loading with partitioning methods proposed in: D Achakeev, B Seeger and P Widmayer: "Sort-based query-adaptive loading of R-trees" in CIKM 2012
